name: Naming Conventions
description: Naming style rules for frontend and backend.

---

Frontend:
- Components: PascalCase (e.g., `PatientForm.tsx`)
- Functions/variables: camelCase
- Hooks: `use` prefix, camelCase (e.g., `usePatientData`)
- Constants: UPPER_SNAKE_CASE
- CSS classes: Tailwind utility-based

Backend:
- Python files, functions, variables: snake_case
- Pydantic and ORM models: PascalCase
- Database tables: snake_case (plural, e.g., `patient_records`)
- API endpoints: kebab-case (e.g., `/api/patient-lookup`)
